title: The (p,n) threshold anomaly in proton elastic scattering on 23Na, 27Al, 31P, 35Cl and 34S.

x4freetext: The (p,n) threshold anomaly in proton elastic
scattering on 23Na, 27Al, 31P, 35Cl and 34S.

x4codes.shortRef: Jour: Nuclear Physics, Section A, Vol.307, p.65 (1978)

x4freetext: The collimated beam intensity was 100 nA.
The following targets were used: NaNO2, Al, Li3PO4,
34S(208Pb) and PbCl2. The thicknesses of the targets
were 100-200 mu-g/cm2.
The excitation functions were normalized to unity at
the threshold minimum.
